Please note that this code is considering the 1D case without diffusion terms. To use ODE45 solver to simulate the full reaction-diffusion model, you could discretize the spatial domain and convert the problem to a system of ODEs. However, using finite difference or finite element methods, as shown in the previous answer, would be more appropriate for the reaction-diffusion model with spatial dependencies.

